pos_mean_info_list.mean: 应纳税的；应征税的；（输入品）应课关税的

word_mean_info__list.difference: 意义较广，多指发自内心的道德伦理上的责任感。
着重指从道义或法律上对事件之后果负责。如：I took full responsibility for breaking the vase.(我承担打破花瓶的全部责任。)
指道义上或法律上对他人的义务，强调强制性。也指因作出承诺而被迫履行的某种义务。
指按道德和法律的标准，一个人永远要尽的义务，强调自觉性。
指因职务或职业关系去履行某种职责。
指任何义务、职责、责任或职务上所尽的本分，强调对他人的责任。

bilingual.target: 缴纳税收是公民的责任。

bilingual.source: Being a juror is a civic duty.
bilingual.target: 成为陪审员是一种公民责任。

bilingual.source: To pay tax is the duty of every citizen.
bilingual.target: 缴税是每个公民的责任。

bilingual.source: It is every citizen's duty to pay taxes.
bilingual.target: 交税是每个公民的责任。

bilingual.source: The police have the duty to enforce the law.
bilingual.target: 警察有责任使生效法律。

bilingual.source: He completed the task out of a sense of duty.
bilingual.target: 他出于责任感完成了任务。

bilingual.source: The government has a duty to protect civil rights.
bilingual.target: 政府有责任保护公民权利。

bilingual.source: The lawyer has a fiduciary duty to his client.
bilingual.target: 律师对他的客户有受托人责任。

bilingual.source: Parents have the duty to take care of their children.
bilingual.target: 父母有责任照顾他们的孩子。

bilingual.source: It is every citizen's duty to follow social norms.
bilingual.target: 遵守社会规范是每个公民的责任。

list.abstract: duty，英文单词，可用作名词，翻译为职责、义务、税收等。
Duty的中文名称是以身作则。是滨崎步的第三张专辑，发行后在日本大热290万张。这张专辑与同时发行的单曲SURREAL，以及一张巡回演唱会DVD，使滨崎步成为第一个同时有三张唱片在Oricon排行达到第一名的歌手。

yingyinNormal.en: Responsibility? Just doing your duty? Is that it?
yingyinNormal.zh: “责任”?尽义务是吧?

yingyinNormal.en: The fairy kingdom is the greatest secret of this land. Our duty is to protect it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 精灵王国是这片土地上最大的秘密，我们的责任就是保护它。

yingyinNormal.en: It is the duty of a true knight to protect and care for those in need. We're off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真正的骑士有责任保护和照顾那些需要帮助的人。我们出发。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: Russell, for assisting the elderly and for performing above and beyond the call of duty,
yingyinNormal.zh: Russell 因为你帮助年长老人，并且表现出至高无上的责任感，

yingyinNormal.en: And so today, you risk yourself? I fulfill my duty. Rally my people. To inspire your strength.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以今天，你是在冒险吗？这是我的责任，鼓舞人民的士气，激发你的力量。

yingyinNormal.en: We want to assure anyone who's considering not voting that it is not only safe to vote, it is your duty to do so.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们希望任何在考虑不投票的各位知道现在投票不仅是安全的，更是你们的责任。

yingyinNormal.en: You have a deep sense of duty, like all the men and women here who served their country, and that's far more important to me than strategy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有很深的责任感，就像这里埋葬的所有为国捐躯的男男女女，这对我来说比策略重要多了。

yingyinNormal.en: If a woman's father is not around, the duty of controlling her base desires falls to the closest male member of her family, in this case, Raj.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果一个女人的父亲不在，那么控制她基本欲望的责任就落在了她最亲的男性亲属身上，也就是拉杰。

yingyinNormal.en: My message this entire campaign has been about serving the country, showing up for duty, and now I'm gonna not show up when the Commander-in-Chief has asked for my help?
yingyinNormal.zh: 整场竞选我传递的信息就是为国家服务，承担责任，现在三军统帅要我帮忙我却拒绝吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I have no idea. He's off-duty. Check around.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道。他下班了。你自己去找找。

yingyinNormal.en: And finally, our first bunny, Officer Hopps. Parking duty. Dismissed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后，第一只兔子，霍普斯警官，交通协管，解散。

yingyinNormal.en: Parisians see it as their duty to enjoy life to its fullest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 巴黎人将尽情享受人生奉为最高圭臬。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the first rule of Hero's Duty? No cuts, no butts, no coconuts?
yingyinNormal.zh: 英雄使命的第一准则是什么? 没有捷径与后悔，只有付出?

yingyinNormal.en: And I was in charge of autopsy duty. No union, no benefits, no nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我负责解剖工作，没有工会，没有福利，啥都没有。

yingyinNormal.en: Our need to stay in power eclipses our duty to govern. That ends tonight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们渴望继续执政而忽视了治国之职，今晚，这到此为止。

yingyinNormal.en: As ambassador to Earth it is my duty to observe and understand Human behavior.
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为被派往地球大使，研究和了解人类行为是我的工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's go. I got an extra guard duty. Today and I'm on KP this morning. So I can't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们走吧。我有额外的执勤，今天上午我得去K.P，以我不能。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, Private Dorchester reporting for duty. You are just so helpful tonight, Gloria.
yingyinNormal.zh: 二等兵多切斯特前来报到，你今晚真是乐于助人啊，歌洛莉亚。

yingyinNormal.en: This is the way I mean to honor my debt to the late Emperor and fulfill my duty to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 此臣所以报先帝而忠陛下之职分也。

yingyinNormal.en: And she brought me this duty-free Toblerone. Oh. I love those. Let's sit somewhere else.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且她还给我带了免税三角巧克力。我好爱吃这个。我们坐别桌吧。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: an action done as part of a job or position

examination_example.sentence: exempt employers from certain <highlight>duties</highlight>
examination_example.sentence_trans: 免除雇主的某些责任

examination_example.sentence: The thought of holding a fixed grin as the camera performed its magical <highlight>duties</highlight> was too much to contemplate.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当摄像机执行其神奇的任务时，一想到要保持一个固定的笑容，就令人难以想象。

examination_example.sentence: The judge failed to tell a jury that it must look at the former governor's decisions on "specific" and "unsettled" issues related to his <highlight>duties</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该法官未能告知陪审团必须考虑前州长就与其职责相关的“特定”、“待定”问题所做出的决策。

sense_info_list.en: the time during which a person must do his or her job
something a person feels he or she ought to do because it is morally right
sense_info_list.zh: 责任; 义务; 本分

examination_example.sentence: As many took on the <highlight>duty</highlight> of trying to integrate reasoning and scientific philosophies into the world, the Renaissance was over.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当许多人承担起将推理和科学哲学融入世界的责任时，文艺复兴就结束了。

word_usage.usage: duty作名词，表示“职责；任务”时，常用复数形式，如：administrative duties 行政职责。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 意为“义务、本分、职责”，指我们对于他人或自己应尽的天职，着重指受内心道德驱使，而非受客观要求所产生的责任感。
意为“责任（感）、义务、负担”，指对某人、公众、社会或某事应负的义务、职责。
意为“义务”，指完成某项协议、诺言或社会要求而必须担当的义务，international obligations意为 “国际义务”。
意为“责任、包袱”，可指“债务（复数形式）”或“缺陷、不利条件（单数形式）”。

sense_info_list.en: something a person feels he or she ought to do because it is morally right

examination_example.sentence: In addition, pop stars or influential people have a <highlight>duty</highlight> to act as positive role models.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 此外，流行明星或有影响力的人有义务充当积极的榜样。

examination_example.sentence: As technology progresses, we all have a <highlight>duty</highlight> to make sure that we shape a future that we would want to find ourselves in.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 随着技术的进步，我们都有责任确保我们塑造一个我们想要的未来。

examination_example.sentence: Students who are burdened with family <highlight>duties</highlight> might choose to take online courses.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 背负着家庭责任的学生可能会选择在线课程。

sense_info_list.en: an action done as part of a job or position

examination_example.sentence: They perform <highlight>duties</highlight> in their owner's best interest.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们以主人的最大利益履行职责。

examination_example.sentence: Make workers less motivated in performing <highlight>duties</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 降低员工履行职责的积极性。

sense_info_list.en: a tax especially on imports into a country

examination_example.sentence: If imported merchandise is unused and destroyed under their supervision, 99% of the <highlight>duties</highlight> paid on the merchandise may be recovered.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果进口商品未被使用并在他们的监督下被销毁，商品的99%的关税可以被收回。

examination_example.sentence: That is why government has historically intervened, banning advertising, imposing health warnings and punitive (惩罚性的) <highlight>duties</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是为什么政府历来干预，禁止广告，施加健康警告和惩罚性的税。

sense_info_list.en: the time during which a person must do his or her job

sense_info_list.zh: 本分; 责任; 义务

examination_example.sentence: But others do double <highlight>duty</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是其他人有双重责任。

examination_example.sentence: The parents had done their <highlight>duty</highlight> and would probably continue to do so.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 父母已经尽到了他们的责任，而且可能还会继续这样做。

examination_example.sentence: One thing is for certain —Larry went above and beyond the call of <highlight>duty</highlight> by getting so close to the burning vehicle!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有一件事是肯定的——拉里如此接近燃烧的汽车，超出了他的职责范围！

examination_example.sentence: As a TV reporter , it’s my <highlight>duty</highlight> to tell the truth to the public.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为一名电视记者，告诉公众真相是我的职责。

examination_example.sentence: Xiao is the <highlight>duties</highlight> a person has to their parents.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 孝是一个人对父母应尽的义务。

examination_example.sentence: Although it’s a public holiday today, some firefighters in our city are still on <highlight>duty</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然今天是公共假日，但我市的一些消防队员仍在执勤。
